[h1]Waymakers[/h1]
[quote]"No settlement should stand alone."[/quote]

[b]⚠️ Requires:[/b] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3271115410]Rails and Roads of the Rim (Continued)[/url]. This mod builds directly on top of RotR's road and rail system and will not work without it.

[b]Roads, railways, and commerce bind isolated peoples together.[/b] Waymakers is a new Ideology meme for builders, traders, and explorers: colonists who believe civilization advances only when people, goods, and ideas are free to move.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mxswat/Waymakers/main/About/dividers/ideology_divider.png[/img]

[b]Infrastructure Required.[/b] Your colony takes a mood hit if it goes 30 days without building a road or railway (new colonies get a grace period). Stay connected, or stay miserable.

[b]Road completion is a celebration.[/b] Finishing a road or railway grants a scaling mood buff (+2 to +30) based on quality tier and length. Better roads, longer roads, bigger payoff.

Incompatible with [b]Isolationist[/b] and [b]Raider[/b]. This is a philosophy of connection, not walls or banditry.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mxswat/Waymakers/main/About/dividers/roles_divider.png[/img]

A new Ideology role for your master builders.
[list]
[*]+50% Construction speed, +20% Mining speed (passive)
[*][b]Coordinate Works[/b] ability. Buffs nearby colonists' construction speed by +75% in a huge radius for 24 hours.
[*]Cast before a caravan departs to double road building work speed on the world map.
[/list]

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mxswat/Waymakers/main/About/dividers/abilities_divider.png[/img]

[b]Coordinate Works[/b]. Rallies the crew, boosting construction speed by +75% in a huge radius for 24 hours. Cast before a caravan departs to speed up road building on the job itself.

[b]Groundbreaking Buff[/b]. Granted by ritual. Temporarily boosts construction speed for all participants, scaling with ceremony quality.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mxswat/Waymakers/main/About/dividers/rituals_divider.png[/img]

[list]
[*][b]Groundbreaking Ceremony.[/b] Kick off a major project with the community behind you.
[*][b]Opening of the Line.[/b] Celebrate a finished road or railway with full pomp and circumstance.
[/list]
Both are led by the Surveyor, fully optional, and scale in quality with participant count and skill.

[b]Translations[/b]
Currently available in English and Italian. More translations welcome, contribute via GitHub.

[b]Support[/b]
Found a bug or have a suggestion? Open an issue on GitHub:
[url]https://github.com/mxswat/Waymakers/issues[/url]

[quote]Subscribe and start paving the way.[/quote]
